args: She won't wake up! Does she have\nthe sleeping sickness?!
(She's clearly in the throes\nof a nightmare...)
(If I don't do something about this,\nthat fiend could end up with her soul!)
Hang on, Notte! I'll save you!
...Is this Notte's dream?\nWhy is it so dark and cold?
I work so hard to make sure everyone has\nhappy dreams, but you forget anyway.
You forget it all! You forget ME!
You are no friend of mine...
YOU ARE NO FRIEND OF MINE!
This is a dream, Notte! The fiend\nis giving you a nightmare!
Don't listen to that false me!
And to think I was THIS close to devouring\na faerie's soul. How unfortunate.
It's the fiend we've been chasing!\nThe one who devours souls\ninside of dreams!
You've been making people have terrible\nnightmares! You hurt my friend Notte!\nAnd I will not stand for it!
Time for you to see what\nnaughty little fiends get!
(Get up... GET UP...\nYou have to save Notte...)
(She's still your dear friend, even if she\nis going to forget all of this...)
(But I won't forget it...\nI'll remember it always!)
